{"tid":1381671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不合作運動？不了 無人既","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:04:37.000Z","uid":106093,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7fc3643cb7122942bffebe57e4551d09c4a3c22","tid":1381671,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:45:53.000Z","msg":"又話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日</span>不合作運動<br />\n無人推 無人開po講<br />\n熱門得一個講緊 但又係啲戇鳩鬧戰<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以向前望下呢<br />\n中共講啲咁既野 <br />\n應該即刻就同佢地攬炒啦<br />\n仲等8月5<br />\n<br />\n係8月5前唔好俾團火停啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平日都要繼續俾壓力上面<br />\n<br />\nBtw 聽日係咪調景嶺..."},{"pid":"50acb7bc681d265582ac64a8e3a243696146ba07","tid":1381671,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:47:18.000Z","msg":"要反省亦要繼續向前<br />\n繼續俾壓力啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1e02d56d0f496c01f1e68ccd0402621976ae64","tid":1381671,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"再加埋全民頭盔<br />\n<br />\n又係無哂人講<br />\n<br />\n聽日齊齊帶埋頭盔出黎啦"},{"pid":"d9246adb637ce7eda0566a064753027ba118ec86","tid":1381671,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"[抗議警黑合作] <br />\n全民港鐵戴頭盔 全民出街戴頭盔 <br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n過左721、727 <br />\n香港人要識保護自己<br />\n要令帶防具 頭盔出行街變成日常<br />\n班狗搜到 都無野講！"},{"pid":"15c4a75cf4f20bc97003828e1dee7c4fec0d18e8","tid":1381671,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:49:05.000Z","msg":"推啊屌"},{"pid":"22eeab0580a1159bc9956d86c8f15e0bb7e785e7","tid":1381671,"uid":106093,"lik